    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require a trailer for transport. The engine currently suffers from a blown head gasket and significant oil leaks, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, the paint is heavily faded with several areas of surface rust, a cracked windshield, and a dented rear bumper. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional air conditioning system. This is strictly a project car or a parts donor for someone with the mechanical expertise to address these substantial issues.",
