    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The exterior is clean and retains a nice shine, though it does have a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips typical of careful, regular use. Inside, the interior is well-kept with only light wear on the seating surfaces and all electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car is solid and drives smoothly, offering a reliable experience for its next owner.",
