      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplar of sustained mechanical integrity and refined engineering. This unit has been maintained to rigorous standards, ensuring a driving experience that remains both responsive and composed. The exterior retains its professional character, while the interior environment reflects a commitment to careful preservation. For the discerning professional seeking a fusion of reliable performance and sophisticated presence, this offering represents a compelling investment in automotive excellence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It runs beautifully and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. The interior is nice and clean, and while there are a few tiny marks here and there from normal use, it still looks fantastic and drives even better! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-focused example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The high-revving NAT-ASP engine breathes through six individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to a 3.62 limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its factory-tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry, ensuring precise turn-in and balanced chassis dynamics. While showing minor cosmetic patina expected of its vintage, the mechanical vitals are strong, with recent rod bearing clearance checks and fresh synthetic fluids throughout. A mechanically sound specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. All systems functional. Serious inquiries only.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory paint, showing a deep luster with only a few minor stone chips and light surface marks consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a clean, non-smoking environment where the premium upholstery remains supple; while there is light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, there are no rips or stains to be found. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. I have retained a comprehensive file of service records, including a recent fluid flush and brake inspection, to ensure the next owner has total peace of mind. It drives straight and true, offering a quiet and composed ride that feels as solid as the day it was first driven. Two sets of keys and the original owner\u2019s manuals are included.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
